    <Note Caller="1" LanguageCode="en" LastEdited="" LastEditedBy="">
      <References>
        <Reference>06600800100004</Reference>
      </References>
      <Content>It is possible that ὅταν occurs in {S:06600800100004} because of the prophetic nature of the context, so that in reality, though the verb is in the past tense, the reference is ultimately to a future event which is indefinite in time. If this is the case, then ὅταν[b] may simply be classified with ὅταν[a] ({D:67.31}).</Content>
